<div class="spell-card">
    <h3>Animal Messenger</h3>
    <p>2nd Level Transmutation</p>
    <p>Casting Time: 1 Action</p>
    <p>Range: 30 Feet</p>
    <p>Components: V, S, M (a morsel of food)</p>
    <p>Duration: 24 Hours</p>
    <p>You choose a Tiny beast you can see within range. The beast must be able to understand you, and it must be willing to deliver a message for you. The message can be up to 25 words long.</p>
    <p>The beast travels for the duration of the spell, moving at its normal speed. When the beast arrives at its destination, it can deliver the message to a creature you specify. The creature can be no more than 5 miles away from you when you cast the spell.</p>
<p>When using this spell at 3rd level or higher duration increases by 48 hours per level above 2nd.</p>
</div>
<div class="spell-card">
    <h3>Barkskin</h3>
    <p>2nd Level Transmutation</p>
    <p>Casting Time: 1 Action</p>
    <p>Range: Touch</p>
    <p>Components: V, S, M (a piece of bark)</p>
    <p>Duration: Concentration, up to 1 hour</p>
    <p>You touch a willing creature. The target's skin becomes tough and bark-like, granting it a +2 bonus to AC for the duration.</p>
    <p>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the bonus to AC increases by 1 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>
</div>
<div class="spell-card">
    <h3>Beast Sense</h3>
    <p>2nd Level Divination (Ritual)</p>
    <p>Casting Time: 1 Action</p>
    <p>Range: Self</p>
    <p>Components: V, S</p>
    <p>Duration: Concentration, up to 1 hour</p>
    <p>You touch a willing beast; for the duration of the spel, you can use your action to see or hear through the beast.</p>
    <p>You can use your action to return to normal human senses during duration.</p>
    <p>While perceiving through the beast you gain any special sensory benefits of the creature but become blind and deaf to your surroundings.</p>
    </div>
